                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
                    <img src="{{ asset('images/why-choose-us.svg') }}" 
                         alt="Pourquoi nous choisir" 
                         class="img-fluid"
                         style="max-height: 500px;">
